                                        ],
                                        "body": "The building shall be safe for human occupancy as determined by the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/pennsylvania/ifc-2021\">International Fire Code</a></span> and the <span class=\"u-italic\">International Property Maintenance Code</span>. Any <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/pennsylvania/iebc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#repair_\">repair</a></span>, <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/pennsylvania/iebc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#alteration_\">alteration</a></span> or <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/pennsylvania/iebc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#change_of_occupancy_\">change of occupancy</a></span> undertaken within the moved structure shall comply with the requirements of this code applicable to the work being performed. Any field-fabricated elements shall comply with the requirements of the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/pennsylvania/ibc-2021\">International Building Code</a></span> or the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/pennsylvania/irc-2021\">International Residential Code</a></span>, as applicable.",
