                                                "body": "The connection of the relocated building to the foundation shall comply with the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/pennsylvania/ibc-2021\">International Building Code</a></span> or the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/pennsylvania/irc-2021\">International Residential Code</a></span>, as applicable.",
