                                        ],
                                        "body": "<div class=\"u-mt-3 u-mb-3\">Buildings shall comply with <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/pennsylvania/ibc-2021\">International Building Code</a></span> or <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/pennsylvania/irc-2021\">International Residential Code</a></span> wind provisions, as applicable.</div><div class=\"u-ml-4\"><div class=\"u-mb-3\"><span class=\"u-font-bold\">Exceptions: </span></div><ol><li>Detached one- and two-family dwellings and Group U occupancies where wind loads at the new location are not higher than those at the previous location.</li><li>Structural elements whose stress is not increased by more than 10 percent.</li></ol></div>",
